OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fwith clear spells and light winds
OL,7,Fleading to a touch of frost. A band of
OL,8,Fcloud and the odd shower will move
OL,9,Feast for a time overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA cold start to the day with
OL,12,Fa frost for some places. It will
OL,13,Fremain dry with plenty of sunshine but
OL,14,Fperhaps some high cloud spreading east
OL,15,Fin the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
