OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FVariable cloud and bright spells with
OL,7,Fsome outbreaks of rain on Wednesday.
OL,8,FRain bands moving east followed by
OL,9,Fdrier and brighter spells for the rest
OL,10,Fof the week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
